{"tid":2298807,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"便衣警涉與兩同袍醫院內虐打病人 辯稱只想「拍醒佢」","createTime":"2020-11-24T10:02:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-26T08:15:33.000Z","uid":56115,"like":3,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"060d8611f483daf334f5e726d7949363d96b58ac","tid":2298807,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T10:02:18.000Z","msg":"去年6月，三名警員涉嫌在北區醫院獨立病房內，以酷刑方式虐打被綁床上的六旬病人，過程被閉路電視拍下。其中兩人昨承認公職人員行為失當罪，還押候懲，餘下一名警員則否認控罪，今出庭自辯，聲稱當時只欲喚醒事主，才會拍他的臉；但他又自言工作壓力大，不想事主醒來，否則「要處理更加多嘅嘢」。他又解釋，首被告只是欲協助他喚醒事主才加入拍臉，次被告則欲抹掉事主的口水，才用事主上衣及床單捂其口鼻。<br />\n<br />\n控方今播放<span class=\"red\">林易昇（31歲）</span>的警誡錄影會面片段。林於片段中透露，其學歷為<span class=\"red\">高級文憑</span>，當時已無業。案發時，林是大埔刑事調查隊隊員，身穿便衣執勤。<br />\n<br />\n法官問林為何離開房間前曾抬頭，林回答指他低頭太久，欲鬆動頸部。法官問他抬頭看甚麼，林答謂：「天花板。」"},{"pid":"697338e2b7f693e52e0add5de70adcdbee3381f6","tid":2298807,"uid":56115,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T10:02:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201124/RA7HULOC5FHCVPXAVHTEQOLMXM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201124%2FRA7HULOC5FHCVPXAVHTEQOLMXM%2F&d=axquv7MewSEsfpkSD3%2FEaBqcspSF5fyAY0%2FEGx5AO9c%3D&h=b0d8ff57\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201124%2FRA7HULOC5FHCVPXAVHTEQOLMXM%2F&h=e36ca366\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201124/RA7HULOC5FHCVPXAVHTEQOLMXM/</a>"},{"pid":"9c19449d188bd4ee744203e02cad93eb9af76c1d","tid":2298807,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T10:05:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0a875dd0f3e9cf50255a3ebe9338fe6b8a1d3a6","tid":2298807,"uid":4917,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T10:08:15.000Z","msg":"個酷刑罪要嚟放響櫃桶底"},{"pid":"ab4941f1c7b02cf41a0992c6ca5bed22ceb86805","tid":2298807,"u